{"tid":2005340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［鬼到⋯］原來謀殺美國既武漢肺炎研究員既殺手 殺完人後就自殺","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T07:36:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0b50343803245e91759d0fef78c92879442614b7","tid":2005340,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎 謀殺案<br />\n<br />\n中文傳媒對Bing Liu呢位 武漢肺炎 研究員被殺案嘅案情研究甚少，好彩我仲有啲美國淵源，我睇完當地地方報紙後，我相信 武漢肺炎 隱藏中國嘅巨大陰謀，唔係完全一啲根據都無。根據 Pittsburgh Post Gazette嘅講法<br />\n<br />\nRoss police believe that Mr. Liu was shot by another man &mdash; identified later by the Allegheny County Medical Examiner&rsquo;s Office as Hao Gu, 46, of Pittsburgh &mdash; who then got into his car parked about 100 yards away on Charlemagne Circle and killed himself.<br />\n<br />\n呢單嘢係擺明有預謀殺完人就自殺，但以下兩段絕對係Key points<br />\n<br />\nPolice declined to disclose a possible motive for the homicide, but they said nothing was stolen from the townhouse and there was no forced entry.<br />\n<br />\nAn autopsy found that Mr. Liu was shot multiple times, including in the head, neck and torso.<br />\n<br />\n大家都意識到呢個係行刑式謀殺，無偷嘢，無Forced entry，分分鐘Liu博士係識Hao Gu，而呢個Hao Gu隨時係為執行黨嘅任務而嚟，美國人摸唔清動機係正路，因為呢單嘢，係必須FBI嚟查，並且FBI嘅情報人員同CIA情報人員交換資料，至可能摸清條友乜水。<br />\n<br />\n而今年二月頭，加拿大一名病毒學者喺非洲離奇死亡，死因無公開，但佢領導P4實驗室，就係中國間諜邱香果夫婦任職。<br />\n<br />\nSource(好似死咗）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post-gazette.com/news/crime-courts/2020/05/04/ross-township-murder-suicide-bing-liu-police-elm-court/stories/202005040082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post-gazette.com%2Fnews%2Fcrime-courts%2F2020%2F05%2F04%2Fross-township-murder-suicide-bing-liu-police-elm-court%2Fstories%2F202005040082&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=c539746c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post-gazette.com/news/crime-courts/2020/05/04/ross-township-murder-suicide-bing-liu-police-elm-court/stories/202005040082</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/30754/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F30754%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25A1%2588&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=21a599f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/30754/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E6%A1%88</a>"},{"pid":"56edcc4fd90ff6663b4c3df080f2009c52324744","tid":2005340,"uid":62826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d545522ce1fdc2a84ed8087e931b448ebd2a8251","tid":2005340,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e538c62cb69cd1927cf4d1dd17e85ddb3098b9b1","tid":2005340,"uid":290879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"JFK咁"},{"pid":"9b16e4c7f72c8a76e51a629ed0d3ef2d4ad1459f","tid":2005340,"uid":72034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"外交部會話佢發現源頭係美國，所以比人殺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf89a14dafab9b51b288f5632ab1fdcca25c63","tid":2005340,"uid":7343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"殺左證人大大聲講then show us <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c29d8130d1212ef6cbd8632abfa3315e37e120","tid":2005340,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"仲要殺佢果個都係支那人"},{"pid":"8f40f09406330adcc4597905b0499b1afa72f3